                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                            oc:textContent "This skill enables extraction of individual frames from video files (MP4, AVI, MOV, etc.) using OpenCV. Extracted frames are saved as image files in a specified output directory. It is suitable for video analysis, creating training datasets, thumbnail generation, and preprocessing video content for further processing." ] ;
